SCIENTIFIC JUSTIFICATION:
WiFi positioning leverages the physical layer characteristics of 802.11 protocols:
- OFDM modulation provides 64-256 subcarriers per channel
- Each subcarrier carries amplitude and phase information
- Human movement causes predictable Doppler shifts
- Multipath propagation creates location-specific interference patterns

Countermeasures work by:
